{"tid":816205,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"綾瀬遙《繼母與女兒的藍調》收視創新高","createTime":"2018-09-12T14:56:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T15:45:42.000Z","uid":126305,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6a2426191274dcee4879b4de99efe37d55a5c74a","tid":816205,"uid":126305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T14:56:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2018/9/1536741887_6d-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2018%2F9%2F1536741887_6d-1280w.jpg&h=d3a9072c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2018/9/1536741896_0l-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2018%2F9%2F1536741896_0l-1280w.jpg&h=aafeb04a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由綾瀬遙、佐藤健、竹野內豐主演，日本近年少有的感人劇《繼母與女兒的藍調》已播近尾聲，昨晚已播到第9集，關東地區收視達17.3%，是首播以來最高收視。至於北海道地區更錄得20.5%收視。<br />\n<br />\n《繼母與女兒的藍調》暫時能夠成為今季最高收視劇集，原因是橋段令人動容，丈夫竹野內豐因癌症離世，綾瀬遙獨力照顧繼女。喪夫悲痛過後，綾瀬遙認識了麵包店老闆佐藤健。在昨晚一集，佐藤健更向綾瀬遙求婚，所以令收視再創新高。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%87%E5%A4%A0%E6%84%9F%E4%BA%BA%E3%80%91%E7%B6%BE%E7%80%AC%E9%81%99%E3%80%8A%E7%B9%BC%E6%AF%8D%E8%88%87%E5%A5%B3%E5%85%92%E7%9A%84%E8%97%8D%E8%AA%BF%E3%80%8B%E6%94%B6%E8%A6%96%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98-141726\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%258A%2587%25E5%25A4%25A0%25E6%2584%259F%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%25B6%25BE%25E7%2580%25AC%25E9%2581%2599%25E3%2580%258A%25E7%25B9%25BC%25E6%25AF%258D%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%2585%2592%25E7%259A%2584%25E8%2597%258D%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E3%2580%258B%25E6%2594%25B6%25E8%25A6%2596%25E5%2589%25B5%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%25AB%2598-141726&d=4bHX7xMxKbaLYX4XVtwEP8KJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=8d2067ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news